events.text: ...this seems wrong, like its just some semantic issue. but i do not see how to argue. th-
then don't. nobody asked you to.
in fact, i would like to ask you not to. i didn't come here to wage war.
war? how is trying to solve a simple material problem war-like?
you invented the problem because something is not to your liking, and you can't accept it.
before you arrived, there was no problem. after you leave, there will be no problem.
the Structure is not false. nor it is true.
stop trying to name it. stop trying to interpret what i say.
everything i say is true, and nothing is meant to be understood.
